OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FTens of thousands of South East Water
OL,8,Fcustomers in Sussex and Kent have been
OL,9,Faffected by the latest supply outage,
OL,10,Fwith around 7,500 still without
OL,11,Fdrinking water for a sixth day.
OL,13,FStorm Goretti, which swept across the
OL,14,FUK last week, disrupted the water
OL,15,Fsupply in the two counties, South East
OL,16,FWater (SEW) said.
OL,18,FResidents are sometimes left unsure as
OL,19,Fto what exactly they are entitled to
OL,20,For what support they can receive when
OL,21,Fwithout supply.
