OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FThe Government has recently updated
OL,8,Fits Guaranteed Standards Scheme (GSS),
OL,9,Fincreasing the amount of compensation
OL,10,Fpeople affected by water outages are
OL,11,Fentitled to.
OL,13,FThe GSS regulations apply to all
OL,14,Fcustomers, and if a company fails to
OL,15,Fmeet any of the guaranteed standards
OL,16,Fset out, you are entitled to a payment.
OL,18,FHere we look at what support and
OL,19,Fcompensation people affected in Sussex
OL,20,Fand Kent may be entitled to:
