OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,F` What should I be told?
OL,9,FWhen water supply is interrupted or
OL,10,Fcut off to carry out works in an
OL,11,Femergency, the company must notify
OL,12,Fcustomers when it is 'reasonably
OL,13,Fpracticable' to do so.
OL,15,FIf a company fails to properly notify
OL,16,Fyou of these details, you may be
OL,17,Fentitled to compensation.
OL,19,F` What water should be provided while
OL,20,Fsupply is interrupted?
