OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FWater companies are entitled to give
OL,8,Fyou free bottled water in the event of
OL,9,Fan outage, providing at least 10
OL,10,Flitres per person per day without
OL,11,Fwater.
OL,13,FThis is usually via bottled water
OL,14,Fcollection points or deliveries.
OL,16,FThere have been reports of sites to
OL,17,Fcollect water being called 'courtesy
OL,18,Fbottled water sites', however, this is
OL,19,Fsomething the company is legally
OL,20,Fobliged to do, rather than being a
OL,21,Fcourtesy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
