OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,F` What compensation am I entitled to?
OL,9,FSEW has said it is 'fully committed to
OL,10,Fcompensating fairly' customers
OL,11,Faffected in the latest outage,
OL,12,Falthough it is unclear exactly how
OL,13,Fmuch at this stage.
OL,15,FIf your supply is not restored within
OL,16,F12 hours of the company finding out
OL,17,Fabout an interruption, you should be
OL,18,Fautomatically paid compensation.
OL,20,FFor every following 12-hour window,
OL,21,Fyou should receive a further payment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
