OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FYou should be paid #50 originally and
OL,8,F#50 for each subsequent 12 hours.
OL,10,FIf any of the guaranteed standards
OL,11,F(GSS) are not met, customers could be
OL,12,Fentitled to up to #2,000 of
OL,13,Fcompensation.
OL,15,FThe exact amount you are entitled to,
OL,16,Fhowever, will depend on the level of
OL,17,Fdisruption and some exemptions may
OL,18,Fapply.
