OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,FAccording to Ofwat, England and
OL,8,FWales's water regulator, companies
OL,9,Fshould automatically make payments
OL,10,Fwhere required, but if they fail to
OL,11,Fpay on time, you could be entitled to
OL,12,Fa further #40 to #100.
OL,14,FFor businesses, these amounts may
OL,15,Fdiffer. For the previous SEW outage
OL,16,Fbetween November 29 and December 4,
OL,17,Fthe firm said it was establishing a
OL,18,F"separate fund", which took the total
OL,19,Fcompensation package for businesses up
OL,20,Fto #2.5 million.
