OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,F` What about exemptions for
OL,8,Fcompensation?
OL,10,FSome exemptions apply to the
OL,11,Fcompensation requirements, including
OL,12,Fwhen an outage has been caused by a
OL,13,Fsevere weather event.
OL,15,FAs the current outage was caused by a
OL,16,Fcombination of factors, rather than
OL,17,Fsolely Storm Goretti, this exemption
OL,18,Fis unlikely to apply.
