OL,3,CWhat are my rights as a South East
OL,4,CWater customer amid latest supply
OL,5,Coutage?
OL,7,F"Leaks and bursts across the network
OL,8,Ffollowing the rapid change in
OL,9,Ftemperature had an impact, as did not
OL,10,Freceiving the usual bulk supply of
OL,11,Ftreated water into our networks", SEW
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe company's customer services
OL,15,Fdirector, Tanya Sephton, said the
OL,16,Fcompany will "provide information on
OL,17,Fboth Guaranteed Standards of Service
OL,18,Fpayments at the earliest opportunity".
